      <p>Are you a volunteer-led group that provides support for people on the streets? We have put together this best practice guide to help you protect the vulnerable adults that use these services, your volunteers and members of the public.</p>
      <p>This toolkit makes it easier for you to develop and be recognised for the quality of your service. The information, training and support provided here supports you to ensure you have adequate standards and safeguarding in place.</p>
